{"id": 2049, "genre": 1000, "title": "为了让你用起来更有安全感，你觉得手机应该增加哪些新功能？", "description": "复杂的社会生活以及手机本身给你带来的不安全感，哪些也许是可以解决的？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 14027, "comment_count": 51, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171205120956w56PdHiVgJesv1ZK.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-05T16:14:59Z", "questions": [{"id": 3389, "title": "为了让你用起来更有安全感，你觉得手机应该增加哪些新功能？", "content": "为了让你用起来更有安全感，你觉得手机应该增加哪些新功能？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 252684, "content": "防窥屏警示，手机被旁边和后面的人偷瞄会有提醒", "image": "img/option/option/20171205165730a2VoU6DulFsv7LOI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252716, "content": "手机被解锁记录查询，密码被对象要去也不怕", "image": "img/option/option/20171205165948orSCGZLfnzQIilvt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252685, "content": "默认开通“被盗之后可以远程删除内容”功能", "image": "img/option/option/20171205170518h4SU2zGB9eEt8nwv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252686, "content": "50%的时候就提醒充电，而不是注意到的时候已经离关机不久了", "image": "img/option/option/20171205170825J0iuYl5OsC8UD6Tr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252687, "content": "电量耗尽的提示更直观，比如使用倒计时预估啥时候关机", "image": "img/option/option/20171205152026GqXviFCEo2WBmDsz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252688, "content": "和门锁相互绑定，出门忘记拿的时候能够收到提示", "image": "img/option/option/20171205171437Iskahf2HSrxQbdp3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252690, "content": "温度不适宜的时候有提示，而不是突然没反应", "image": "img/option/option/20171205171318EIRhvnpteSJZCMHw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252743, "content": "定时虚拟来电 or 虚拟短信功能，聚会前设好，随时脱身", "image": "img/option/option/20171205172035O7eJ6Vrq9y4NxaRd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}